comments: Replay review of the foul called on Brown Jr. (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Brown initiates lower body contact with Rozier (CHA) that affects his follow-through.
Towns (MIN) and Bridges (CHA) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Richards (CHA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Towns (MIN) slides his left pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Miller (CHA) legally contests Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) and Rozier (CHA) pursue the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs during rebounding.
Gobert (MIN) cleanly blocks Richards' (CHA) shot attempt.
Richards (CHA) moves into Conley's  (MIN) path and initiates body contact as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) moves alongside Bridges' (CHA) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) commits a take foul on Conley (MIN).
Rozier (CHA) slightly extends his right leg forward and marginal lower body contact occurs with Anderson (MIN) during the jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Bridges (CHA) moves laterally into Conley's (MIN) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Bridges (CHA) and Brown Jr. (MIN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Hayward (CHA) commits a take foul on Alexander-Walker (MIN).
